message.body: Hi. Would you like to do a yoga class then get some food on Tuesday?
I'm doing well. Ella went with Girl Scouts to the penn museum. Getting spring cleaning done, listening to records. How are you? How is yoga?
That sounds so nice. Do you have any cookies you're selling? Yoga is good. I like my classmates. It's a warm environment. Everyone is trying to be a bett
That's so nice. Is today the last day? I do still have cookies. Peanut butter, mint, coconut, shortbread, lemon.
Can I order mint and coconut? How much are they? The program goes until June.
Thats great! And of course you can. They are four bux a box.
I'm excited for yoga, I haven't gone once this semester, feeling stuff
Great! We can to a 5:45 in old city or a 6:15 in cc.
